(3006, 'Contraseed 100mg 12 vag.ovule', 'كونتراسيد 12 اقماع مهبلية', '', '18', 'Nonoxynol', 'International trading pharmaceuticals laboratoires > the international co. for trading and investement', 'Unknown', 'غير محدد', 'لبوس منع حمل قا تل للحيوانات المنوية', 'Surfactant spermicide', '100mg', 'indication nonoxynol 9 is a surfactant spermicide used for contraception in spermicidal creams jellies foams gel and lubricants. it is also used in conjuction with other methods of contraception including condoms cervical caps and diaphragms. mechanism of', '', '', 5376, '2023-02-05', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
