(12665, 'Xanthistop 80 mg 30 tablets', 'زانثيستوب 80 مجم 30 قرص', '120', '147', 'Febuxostat', 'Sedico > inspire pharmaceutical company', 'Tablet', 'أقراص', 'علاج النقرص -- تقليل التهابات المفاصل و العظام -- تقليل الالام الركبة والكعبين', 'Antigout', '80 mg', 'Febuxostat is indicated for the chronic management of hyperuricemia in adult patients with gout who have an inadequate response to a maximally titrated dose of [allopurinol], who are intolerant to allopurinol, or for whom treatment with allopurinol is not advisable.[L46073] It is not recommended for the treatment of asymptomatic hyperuricemia [L32238] or secondary hyperuricemia.[A230583]', '6224000866297', '', 12027, '2024-07-10', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
